Yahi Hai Global Ordering Problem

Tum expect kar rahe ho:

MY
NAME
IS
ANURAG

Ye kehlata hai:

Global Ordering  i.e  Entire Topic ke sab messages ka order preserve rehna.

Kafka multiple partitions me: Global Ordering Guarantee Nahi Karta

Partition Ordering Kya Hai?

Partition-0

Offset 0: "MY"
Offset 1: "ANURAG"

Partition-1

Offset 0: "NAME"
Offset 0: "Pandey"

Partition-2

Offset 0 : "IS"


Kafka sirf itna guarantee karta hai:

"MY" hamesha "ANURAG" se pehle aayega 
and 
"NAME" hamesha "Pandey" se pehle aayega 


Lekin Kafka ye guarantee nahi karta ki:

MY -> NAME -> IS -> ANURAG

isi order me hi mile.


